--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DEPENDENCIES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To compile you will need the following dependencies:
(These are listed as Ubuntu packages. You may need to adjust for your distribution.)

automake
libglib2.0-dev
libx11-dev
valac-0.26 
libgranite-dev
libsqlite3-dev
libgee-0.8-dev
libc6-dev
libgtk-3-dev
libtool

(sudo apt-get install libtool libgtk-3-dev libc6-dev libgee-0.8-dev libsqlite3-dev libgranite-dev valac-0.26 libx11-dev libglib2.0-dev automake)

(Other versions of valac may work. But newer versions seems to have a bug that prevents compiling)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
BUILDING AND INSTALLING
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
mkdir build
cd build
../autogen.sh
make
sudo make install

You can test the program by running
src/relay
